extends _layout.jade

block header
  //- - var page = {current: 'about_en.html' ,other: 'about.html', lang: 'en'}
  - var current = 'about_en.html' 
  - var other = 'about.html'
  - var lang = 'en'
  include partials/_header.jade

block content  
  .page-english
    section.about
      .jumbotron.jumbotron-fluid.p-0
        .bg-wrapper.about-wrapper
          .container
            .card
              hgroup.section-header.my-3.my-lg-3
                h2.mb-0.mb-lg-3 Company
              .row
                .col-lg-6.order-1
                  div
                    img.w-100.lazy(data-src='images/company-intro1.jpg', alt='')
                .col-lg-6.order-2
                  .p-3.p-md-0
                    hgroup.section-header
                      h3.lead.text-primary.mt-0 More than 30 years of design and planning experience in the paper making industry. Biguar Machine Technology Wuxi Co., Ltd. is a professional machine manufacturing company, with high-quality equipment, expert measuring methods, and are dedicated to extensive training and professional development of our employees.
                    .intro-text
                      p
                        | New factory funded in 2017, located in the Hu Tai Industrial Zone, Wuxi, Jiangsu in the Yangtze River Delta Economic Zone - the most developed area of China. We specialize in manufacturing paper making preparation equipment, paper pulp molding equipment, together with development and manufacture of molds.
                .w-100.order-3.my-0.my-lg-3
                .col-lg-6.order-3.order-lg-4
                  .p-3.p-md-0
                    img.w-100.lazy(data-src='images/company-intro2.jpg', alt='')
                .col-lg-6.order-4.order-lg-3
                  .p-3.p-md-0
                    .intro-text
                      p
                        | Due to huge biodegradable product requirement, paper pulp molding market rapid growth in market demand. We setup this new facility to developing new paper molding process technology, manufacturing high efficient stock preparation equipment and high throughput forming machine.
                        br
                        | Based upon customers’ needs and demands, we customized everything from the process flow and the design of the factory, the equipment design and production, to the installation and construction of machinery. The Biguar team has the ability to provide the best technology and service to help our customers perfect and successfully carry out their plans.
    section#spirit-intro.spirit-intro.pt-5
      .container
        .spirit-wrapper
          .row.justify-content-center.align-items-center
            .col-lg-6
              hgroup.section-header.mt-0
                h2 Philosophy
                h3.h2.lead.text-primary.mt-0
                  | Persistence of products innovation and development
                  br
                  | Keep ability to adapt and adjust to the market evolution
                  br
                  | Our insistence on becoming industry bellwether
              .intro-text
                p
                  | Each Biguar’s member is following the principle of Aggressive, Pragmatic, Innovate, Cooperate,
                  br
                  | constantly innovates the new technology, using the core competence to give the product a whole new life.
                  br
                  | Adopting a market oriented approach, providing high-quality production equipment, to help customers produce superior and advantageous products is our mission.
            .col-lg-6.order-lg-first
              img.lazy.img-fluid(data-src='images/spirit-intro.jpg', alt='')
    section#technology.technology
