            .col-md-6
              .intro-text
                li.text-white Complete system integration planning, all team members are the elite in the paper making industry.
                li.text-white 3D CAD/CAM design system with simulation analysis.
                li.text-white Best location in China for large & heavy machining, complete satellite factories supply chain.
                li.text-white World leading forming machine, tolerance up to 0.02mm.
                li.text-white In-house experienced electrical engineer, customized programmable PCL
